{"tid":321511,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺係香港大雞大屌羸其他台灣炸雞?","createTime":"2017-07-14T08:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T02:49:08.000Z","uid":52539,"like":60,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15ad9f054ebaba4871f40ebc48cca83f4f220d91","tid":321511,"uid":52539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T08:42:29.000Z","msg":"大雞大 CP值高20幾蚊大大蕭 肉質夠哂滑 多肉汁 仲要幫你切埋加埋D辣粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBB雞 王者雞腿排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係街勁遠行埋黎已經閒到大雞大既味道<br />\n<br />\n相反 豪大 屌你三十幾蚊 D肉只不過係壓平睇落大D 味道比較單一 乾冇乜肉汁 同因為太大塊關係D粉唔平均會搞到一邊勁鹹一邊冇乜味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n繼光香香雞就的確做到夠乾身 D油迫哂出去 食落比較健康 但食炸雞食咁健康做乜尻? 炸埋D雞胸肉 乜野肉汁都冇 柴皮 不過你話要食得健康 我都吹你唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但唔知點解大雞大愈執愈多 得番勁少分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a00f1547241be1f57b18f855af869a4f4f49311","tid":321511,"uid":12628,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:04:29.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母大雞大！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以可以開多幾間分店呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48d40c1e13c34490ea40cf7aee90b2f604b2e8f","tid":321511,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislik